(149, 'Zero-waste: The women in Asia who gave up plastic', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-48513628', 'China, Indonesia and Vietnam are among the worst polluters for plastic waste being dumped in the ocean. Meet the women in those countries trying to change that.', 'http://c.files.bbci.co.uk/1539F/production/_107234968_p07c7drd.jpg', 'Tue, 04 Jun 2019 23:02:35 GMT', 'BBC', 'science'),
