(346, 'Saudi Arabia and the arms race that you\'ve not heard enough about', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/bx0_r6_kMgE/index.html', 'It\'s the Middle East arms race that many people don\'t want to talk about. The White House may be preoccupied with Iran\'s past pursuit of nuclear weapons and its present strategic status in the region. But simmering nearby is another rapid militarization, conducted by a favored family of the White House, the House of Saud.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/181130163724-01-trump-mbs-split-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(347, '17 killed in Dubai bus crash', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/r1hM7eSX6HQ/index.html', 'Seventeen people were killed Thursday evening when a bus crashed into an overhead road sign in Dubai, according to police.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190607054530-dubai-bus-crash-0607-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(348, 'Multinational investigation says \'state actor\' responsible for attacks on Gulf oil tankers', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/OK6eRAQvzXI/index.html', 'The initial findings of an international investigation into attacks on four oil tankers off the coast of the United Arab Emirates in May has concluded that a \"state actor\" is the most likely culprit.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190513131435-01-oil-tanker-sabotage-0513-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(349, 'Shirin Ebadi Fast Facts', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/Atxwj_nHf9E/index.html', 'View CNN\'s Fast Facts about the life of Shirin Ebadi, the first Muslim woman to win the Nobel Peace Prize.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/160408142449-shirin-ebadi-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(350, 'Here\'s what you need to know about Eid al-Fitr, one of Islam\'s biggest holidays', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/thEOcJNS7ns/index.html', 'More than one billion Muslims around the world will celebrate Eid al-Fitr this week, as the month-long Ramadan fast ends and the festivities begin. The celebrations mark a time when communities within the Muslim world come together.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/180615152307-18-eid-2018-unfurled-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(351, 'Hezbollah\'s chief says a US strike against Iran will spur regional conflict, leading American forces to be \'annihilated\'', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/hws8VTARlSo/index.html', 'Hezbollah\'s leader warned the United States against striking Iran, saying if it does \"the entire region will burn.\"', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/130501125138-hezbollah-chief-hassan-nasrallah-vertical-large-gallery.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(352, 'Saudi Arabia united the Arab world against Iran. That means conflict could be one step closer', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/6JRCYFYMjtE/index.html', 'King Salman of Saudi Arabia has pulled off in Mecca what many had thought unlikely -- getting 20 or so disparate Arab nations to unite in a common position against Iran. It is a milepost on a road that may yet lead to regional conflict.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190530234247-0530-king-salman-mecca-summmit-01-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(353, 'For residents of Syria\'s last rebel-held province, no place is safe', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/BDUlqpkpXw8/index.html', 'NO_DESCRIPTION', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190531103758-02-syria-ariha-0527-restricted-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(354, 'Israel faces new elections after Netanyahu fails to build coalition', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/37mUKEfxRkA/index.html', 'Israel will hold new national elections in late summer after Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu failed to put together a coalition government from the parties elected to parliament on April 9th.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190529171511-netanyahu-knesset-0529-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(355, 'Satellite images reveal strikes on Syria\'s Idlib province', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/G6dOQRpceYA/index.html', 'Airstrikes and fighting in Syria\'s last rebel-held province have left a trail of damage visible from space. In satellite images from May 20 and May 26, swathes of fields in northwestern Idlib appear blackened, the neat lines of city streets and blocks become blurs of debris, and plumes of smoke dot the landscape.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190528133204-02-idlib-satellite-0526-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(356, 'Captured ISIS fighter says he helped imprison James Foley and Alan Henning', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/GX_1gszuN4g/index.html', 'Alexanda Kotey, a former ISIS fighter accused of forming one of the group\'s most notorious terror cells, admitted he was responsible for overseeing the imprisonment of western hostages James Foley,  Alan Henning and John Cantlie.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/180409153218-01-beatles-isis-npw-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(357, 'How \'document hunters\' spirited thousands of government files out of Syria', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/1B2veGEaav8/index.html', 'Col. Anwar R. worked for Syria\'s intelligence services until he defected in 2012. He fled to abroad, but eventually his history caught up with him. He\'s one of the first big catches for investigators who have smuggled hundreds of thousands of government documents out of war zones.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/130830171021-bashar-al-assad-red-paint-vertical-large-gallery.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(358, 'Iran\'s Nuclear Capabilities Fast Facts', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/eaeyn3bldSA/index.html', 'Read CNN\'s Fast Facts on Iran\'s nuclear capabilities.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/141125164236-iran-nuclear-talks-flag-missile-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(359, 'Trump dances with danger in Middle East by deploying aircraft carrier and a peace plan', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/6Gkjq9qkR_M/index.html', 'In the Persian Gulf, a US aircraft carrier, the USS Abraham Lincoln, lurks off the Iranian coast, sending out a message of aggression. Meanwhile, in the Levant, the administration of US President Donald Trump starts to roll out his version of a widely anticipated peace plan for the Israelis and the Palestinians.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190506102709-uss-abraham-lincoln-file-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(360, 'Iranian police arrest 30 people during yoga class', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/1CWikfWbaAE/index.html', 'Authorities in Iran arrested 30 people as they took part in a private yoga class in Gorgan, a city in the north of the country, according to an official news agency, the Young Journalists Club.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190524094818-yoga-mats-stock-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(361, 'Iran refuses Trump\'s offer of talks unless US shows \'respect\'', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/7dXaZOQ7suE/index.html', 'Iran\'s Foreign Minister, Mohammad Javad Zarif, has said his country won\'t negotiate with President Donald Trump unless the US shows Tehran \"respect\" by honoring its commitments under the disputed nuclear deal.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/171006094430-01-mohammad-javad-zarif-file-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(362, 'Starving Yemen\'s drug problem', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/HCDKsjALHOk/index.html', 'Most Yemenis chew khat to get through their hungry, war-ravaged days. But that demand doesn\'t help the country address its food crisis.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190520122647-yemen-khat-harvest-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(363, 'CNN exposes systematic abuse of aid in Yemen', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/Cys8IaFbkGQ/index.html', 'Tens of thousands of people are going hungry in Houthi-controlled Yemen as desperately needed food aid is diverted away from them, a CNN investigation finds.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190523081709-yemen-thumb-2-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east'),
(364, 'UN threatens to suspend food aid in Yemen after CNN investigation', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_meast/~3/XYCRfCvaZm0/index.html', 'The United Nations is threatening to suspend aid that helps thousands of destitute Yemenis following a CNN investigation that exposed the theft or \"diversion\" of food aid by Houthi rebels.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190510105521-yemen-issham-beshir-super-169.jpg', 'NO_DATE', 'CNN', 'middle_east');
