(990, '\'Black Mirror\' reflects uneven nature in Anthony Mackie and Miley Cyrus episodes', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/eCNjZ4uk7cU/index.html', '\"Black Mirror\" tends to be a hit-miss proposition, and isn\'t above doing a little old-fashioned pandering to get attention. So it is with a Goldilocks-like three-episode flight of the anthology that consists of a near-perfect installment starring Anthony Mackie, a tense but minor one about a tech company and a relatively weak vehicle about a pop star, and her alter ego, featuring Miley Cyrus.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190603084959-black-mirror-miley-cyrus-super-169.jpg', 'Wed, 05 Jun 2019 12:29:05 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment'),
(991, 'What Keanu Reeves should do next', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/4jQmtKiyvvU/index.html', 'America\'s (er, and Canada\'s?) immortal sweetheart Keanu Reeves is everywhere right now.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/140902152925-keanu-reeves-09022014-vertical-large-gallery.jpg', 'Wed, 05 Jun 2019 21:19:46 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment'),
(992, 'The improv behind \'Always Be My Maybe\'', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/I0B4z-4X7g0/index.html', 'One of the best scenes in \"Always Be My Maybe,\" the Netflix rom-com starring Ali Wong and Randall Park, features a cameo by Keanu Reeves.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190529083409-always-be-my-maybe-netflix-super-169.jpg', 'Sun, 02 Jun 2019 17:32:50 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment'),
(993, '\'The Handmaid\'s Tale\' feels the weight of its timeliness', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/FsXyLX5UDIU/index.html', '\"The Handmaid\'s Tale\" isn\'t the best TV show ever, although it\'s plenty good. But it\'s hard to think of a series that has been better calibrated to tap into the zeitgeist and unease of its cultural and political moment.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190531121219-the-handmaids-tale-season-3-super-169.jpg', 'Mon, 03 Jun 2019 16:00:36 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment'),
(994, '\'Dark Phoenix\' fails to ignite latest version of X-Men saga', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/VIjykmflCwA/index.html', 'The Phoenix Saga in the X-Men comics of the 1970s is rightly considered a classic of the genre, which explains why filmmakers keep returning to it. Yet the hope for a truly definitive take on the story, \"Dark Phoenix,\" proves a tepid addition to the \"X-Men\" cinematic series, while possessing just enough merit to prevent entirely going down in flames.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190531121501-dark-phoenix-xmen-super-169.jpg', 'Wed, 05 Jun 2019 12:32:52 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment'),
(995, '\'When They See Us\' makes a powerful case to be seen', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/nfa4TPpf1oY/index.html', 'The miscarriage of justice that surrounded the Central Park Five should by now be well known, but the details of the case, as reenacted, provide the inherent power of \"When They See Us,\" a Netflix miniseries that\'s strongest at the beginning and end and sags somewhat in the middle.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190528083921-when-they-see-us-netflix-super-169.jpg', 'Thu, 30 May 2019 13:28:43 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment'),
(996, '\'Godzilla\' brings more smoke than fire to the \'Monsterverse\'', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/-sfjTmTRoGQ/index.html', '\"Godzilla: King of the Monsters\" rekindles a 1950s subtitle, but this latest addition to Warner Bros.\' ambitious plans to create a lucrative \"Monsterverse\" generates more smoke than actual fire.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190523094930-godzilla-king-of-the-monsters-super-169.jpg', 'Tue, 28 May 2019 21:05:29 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment'),
(997, 'Adam Levine may have quit \'The Voice,\' but you can catch him on tour this summer', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/hI-oGtwsLDc/index.html', 'Adam Levine may be gone from \"The Voice,\" but he\'s hitting the road with Maroon 5 over the summer (and saving rhinos over on his Instagram in the meantime.)', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190524150356-adam-levine-lead-02-super-169.jpg', 'Thu, 30 May 2019 17:54:03 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment');
